0.1.name: wordpress/multipowupload
0.1.description: Fast and simple way to upload images and other files. * Automatically resize and upload pictures for your blog. * Allow to generate thumbnails on client side and upload them to server. * Rotate, crop operations, 3 resize modes, configurable thumbnails dimensions, watermarking. * List and thumbnails view. Plugin will replace build-in WordPress flash uploader.
